snippet.title: Where are you, Cinderella? | Trailer EN
snippet.description:
Discover a new Cinderella adventure at the heart of the world of showbiz and Vietnamese culture!
Here is the trailer for the visual novel Where are you, Cinderella? 

The game will be available for free on PC and Mobile.


► Demos
https://kiminako.itch.io/where-are-you-cinderella
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kiminako.wayc
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2416930/Where_are_you_Cinderella/

► Social networks
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KimiNako
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TKA_KimiNako
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kiminako.art/

#Cinderella #VisualNovel #WAYC
